highlights.text: “Selalu Ada di Nadimu - Original Soundtrack From "JUMBO"” by Prince Poetiray and Quinn Salman is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #1.
“Jhol” by Maanu and Annural Khalid has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 151 days straight.
MXZI has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “MONTAGEM TOMADA - Slowed” is the highest at #10.
“My Bubble Gum” by Rasheeda is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 6 spots at #20.
